{
  "text": "Furthermore, Biofeedback Nexus 10 was a precise and useful tool for monitoring heart rate and skin conductance, physiological parameters which, together with other measurements of monitorable autonomic parameters, can be considered stress indicators in situations that generate anxiety [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , as was the case at the point of administering anesthesia in this research.",
  "correct_citation": {
